<%- content_for(:title) do %>
Thank you for applying to Devschool, the premiere online web development school!
<%- end %>

<%- content_for(:canonical) do %>
https://devschool.rocks/applied
<%- end %>

<div class="full-bg full-applied"
     style="background: url(<%= image_path('heroes/applied-bg.jpg') %>) no-repeat 50% 50% fixed;">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12 above-fold">
        <h1>Thank you for applying to Devschool! You have taken the first step in an amazing adventure!</h1>
	<h2><a data-scroll href="#below-the-fold">Scroll down</a> to see what your next steps are</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container" id="below-the-fold">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12 below-fold">
      <h2 class="headline">So you have applied.. what now?</h2>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3">
      <p class="tailline">Please take a moment to tweet or share on facebook your awesome decision to apply to Devschool - we give priority to applications to mention us on social media!.</p>
      <div class="block-center">
      <div style="margin-left: 20%; width: 80%; text-align: center;">
        <a class="twitter-share-button" href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?button_hashtag=devschoolrocks&text=I%20just%20applied%20at%20https%3A%2F%2Fdevschool.rocks%20to%20become%20a%20web%20developer!" class="twitter-hashtag-button" data-size="large" data-related="devschoolrocks">Tweet it!</a>
        <div class="fb-share-button" data-href="http://www.katalpa.cz" data-layout="button"></div>
        <div class="g-plus" data-action="share"></div>
      </div>
      </div>
    <h3 class="headline">Self Starters ROCK!</h3>
    <ul class="list-group">
      <li class="list-group-item">Check out our friends at <a rel="nofollow" href="https://codeschool.com">Codeschool</a> and take the
        free <a href="https://www.codeschool.com/courses/front-end-foundations">HTML</a>,
        <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.codeschool.com/courses/try-ruby">Ruby</a>,
        and <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.codeschool.com/paths/javascript">JavaScript</a> courses.</li>
      <li class="list-group-item">Create yourself a <a href="https://github.com/join">Github profile</a> to show off what you are learning,
        and of course take the free <a href="https://www.codeschool.com/courses/try-git" rel="nofollow">Git</a> course at
      Codeschool!</li>
      <li class="list-group-item">Create a <a rel=nofollow href="https://learn.co/join/web-prework">Learn.co</a> where you can do
        some web development setup prework - they require a Mac, but so do we.</li>
    </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
